					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Here's a minor suggestion, you don't need to take it...
<br />
<br />In Super Mario 1, if Luigi gets a fire flower, he is indistinguishable from firey Mario.  I always thought that was annoying to no end.
<br />
<br />So if you are going to change which palette a character is using, I would suggest that you make it blink between their normal colors and the "I have fire" palette, so you can still tell which character is which.</div>

					
